<!-- ─── FAQ ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="section section-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>When does each issue arrive?</summary>
        <p>Every Monday morning before 7 AM Eastern. You'll have it before your first client call of the week.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>What markets are covered?</summary>
        <p>The Greater Toronto Area — both the 416 (City of Toronto) and the 905 region (Mississauga, Brampton, Markham, Vaughan, Oakville, Burlington, and surrounding markets). Data sourced from TRREB.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I cancel anytime?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Cancel from your account page at any time — you'll retain access through the end of your current billing period, then your subscription ends. No questions asked.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Can I access back issues?</summary>
        <p>Yes. Active subscribers have full access to the complete archive of every issue ever published.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>Is this affiliated with TRREB or any brokerage?</summary>
        <p>No. The Real Scoop is an independent publication. Data is sourced from publicly available TRREB reports and compiled into a clean, readable format.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="faq-item">
        <summary>How is my payment handled?</summary>
        <p>Payments are processed securely by Stripe. We never see or store your card details. Your subscription renews automatically each month until you cancel.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

